=Yummy Yummy Yummy=

2
00:01:41,020 --> 00:01:43,900
=Episode 30=

3
00:01:50,740 --> 00:01:53,700
(Xuanzheng Hall)

4
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:56,910
Who are you?

5
00:02:00,240 --> 00:02:03,520
I am Grand Princess Fuhui of Protection,

6
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:05,910
sent by His Majesty,

7
00:02:05,910 --> 00:02:08,120
bearing the Imperial Seal,

8
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:11,080
(Xuanzheng Hall)
to denounce Prince Zhao's treason.

9
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:12,900
Prince Zhao has committed high treason.

10
00:02:13,480 --> 00:02:14,920
All of the Li clan

11
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,710
have the right to punish him.

12
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,030
If you continue to obstruct,

13
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,920
you will share his guilt.

14
00:02:21,920 --> 00:02:23,800
You will be executed,

15
00:02:24,310 --> 00:02:26,120
and all your clans will be exterminated.

16
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:29,400
If you lay down your weapons now,

17
00:02:30,060 --> 00:02:31,990
His Majesty will deal
with you leniently.

18
00:02:43,920 --> 00:02:44,870
Lin Yan,

19
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,920
you're not dead.

20
00:02:49,270 --> 00:02:51,480
The Li clan's target for punishment

21
00:02:51,710 --> 00:02:53,270
is probably someone else.

22
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:55,360
The people will only know

23
00:02:56,420 --> 00:02:58,640
that the Grand Princess
and the Crown Prince

24
00:02:58,940 --> 00:03:00,120
conspired to commit treason.

25
00:03:00,450 --> 00:03:01,310
Guards,

26
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,100
kill Princess Fuhui

27
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:04,290
and seize the seal.

28
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,270
Yes.

29
00:03:13,480 --> 00:03:14,550
Lin Yan,

30
00:03:14,830 --> 00:03:15,670
I raised you

31
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:17,990
for 17 years.

32
00:03:18,150 --> 00:03:19,590
17 years.

33
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,310
Yet you're so ungrateful

34
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:25,080
and go against me.

35
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,710
You have trapped yourself

36
00:03:27,710 --> 00:03:29,080
in this deadly situation.

37
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,960
Well,

38
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,520
you somewhat resemble

39
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:35,960
my eldest son,

40
00:03:36,990 --> 00:03:37,830
so I'll grant you

41
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:39,710
a whole body in death.

42
00:03:47,710 --> 00:03:48,960
You are not Lin Yan.

43
00:03:51,680 --> 00:03:52,960
Where is Lin Yan?

44
00:03:54,180 --> 00:03:55,020
So,

45
00:03:55,620 --> 00:03:56,940
your father was

46
00:03:56,940 --> 00:03:59,580
the celebrated Prefect back then?

47
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:01,740
Yes.

48
00:04:02,140 --> 00:04:03,170
Prince Zhao exterminated

49
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:04,700
your entire clan.

50
00:04:05,060 --> 00:04:06,860
Prince Zhao is plotting treason,

51
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,770
and you'll stand against him?

52
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:10,700
Yes.

53
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,460
Why do you trust me so much?

54
00:04:13,300 --> 00:04:14,700
Such a shocking secret.

55
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:17,180
If I reported it to Prince Zhao

56
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:18,840
and he succeeded,

57
00:04:19,770 --> 00:04:21,580
I could rise to power easily.

58
00:04:22,340 --> 00:04:23,180
Would you?

59
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,260
Li Ji betrayed his friend

60
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,620
and was despised by the world.

61
00:04:30,670 --> 00:04:32,660
I would never do such a thing.

62
00:04:34,220 --> 00:04:35,460
In this life,

63
00:04:35,670 --> 00:04:36,700
to have a true friend,

64
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,220
to kill a traitor,

65
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:40,540
to live and sing,

66
00:04:41,140 --> 00:04:41,980
that is enough.

67
00:04:45,820 --> 00:04:46,700
He's on the road

68
00:04:46,700 --> 00:04:48,700
to send you to the netherworld to atone.

69
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:52,060
(Prince Zhao's Mansion)

70
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,180
Mr. Lu,

71
00:05:19,820 --> 00:05:21,380
Prince Zhao has succeeded.

72
00:05:21,820 --> 00:05:22,660
Do you think

73
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:25,300
he will consider you a threat?

74
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,620
Noble Consort Dou is related to you,

75
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:30,180
but she won't protect you.

76
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:31,340
You should know

77
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:33,260
that today,
Prince Zhao is trying to kill

78
00:05:33,540 --> 00:05:35,580
his own siblings.

79
00:05:37,900 --> 00:05:40,020
You're familiar
with the Yong'an Code, right?

80
00:05:41,260 --> 00:05:43,220
You only know
that treason is a capital offense,

81
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:45,260
but Article 13 of the Yong'an Code

82
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:46,900
clearly states

83
00:05:47,540 --> 00:05:49,260
that those who report treason

84
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:51,420
may have their sentences reduced,

85
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:52,820
depending on the info they provide.

86
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:55,620
You mean,

87
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,220
I have a chance to survive?

88
00:05:57,560 --> 00:06:00,020
I only want
to bring Prince Zhao to justice.

89
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:05,260
Prince Zhao will besiege the Palace.

90
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,260
To prevent news from leaking,

91
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,340
after he succeeds,

92
00:06:11,420 --> 00:06:13,640
he will claim that the Crown Prince
committed treason,

93
00:06:13,820 --> 00:06:15,230
and he has to kill him.

94
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:17,620
The Noble Consort
will support this claim.

95
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:19,700
But to control the Noble Consort,

96
00:06:21,980 --> 00:06:23,980
Prince Zhao
has kept their correspondence

97
00:06:26,260 --> 00:06:28,460
hidden in the study of Fuyi Manor.

98
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,060
Thank you.

99
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:36,980
By the way,

100
00:06:37,660 --> 00:06:38,580
the Yong'an Code

101
00:06:38,780 --> 00:06:40,140
only has 12 articles.

102
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:46,500
12 articles?

103
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:49,940
Lin Yan,

104
00:06:50,260 --> 00:06:51,660
how dare you trick me?

105
00:06:51,910 --> 00:06:53,300
You will not die a good death.

106
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:55,740
(Complete and Bright)

107
00:07:19,020 --> 00:07:24,500
(Prince Zhao's Mansion)

108
00:07:50,580 --> 00:07:52,300
Mr. Lin and I

109
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:56,020
anticipated today's events.

110
00:07:56,820 --> 00:08:00,220
We had the Sixteen Guards ready.

111
00:08:00,900 --> 00:08:03,820
I risked my life

112
00:08:03,910 --> 00:08:06,180
to make you let your guard down

113
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:08,340
and send all your men out.

114
00:08:09,140 --> 00:08:10,180
Otherwise,

115
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:11,580
if you still had

116
00:08:11,580 --> 00:08:13,340
one or two men left,

117
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:16,180
they'd harm the commoners.

118
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,340
Mr. Lin has gone to Suishui City.

119
00:08:22,300 --> 00:08:23,580
He must've obtained

120
00:08:23,580 --> 00:08:25,940
the evidence of your communication
with Noble Consort Dou.

121
00:08:26,420 --> 00:08:27,700
You cannot escape

122
00:08:28,580 --> 00:08:29,860
the charge of treason.

123
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:35,020
The military tally is in my hands.

124
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:37,140
All generals, listen.

125
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:40,820
Today, Prince Zhao
must be brought to justice.

126
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:51,900
(Xuanzheng Gate)

127
00:09:13,980 --> 00:09:15,780
Save the Prince!

128
00:09:15,780 --> 00:09:17,460
Kill!

129
00:10:07,100 --> 00:10:07,940
Let's go.

130
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:09,060
Go.

131
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:20,540
Oh, no.

132
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:35,020
Hurry, hurry.

133
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,860
Finally, I've rescued all of you.

134
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:38,660
Or my young master would be anxious.

135
00:10:38,770 --> 00:10:40,140
You'll be out of the Palace soon.

136
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:41,260
I have to go back.

137
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:42,380
I can only take you this far.

138
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:43,700
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

139
00:10:43,700 --> 00:10:44,640
Take care of yourselves.

140
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:50,260
- Go.
- Hurry, go.

141
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:51,100
Yangyang.

142
00:10:58,500 --> 00:10:59,900
Prince Zhao, Li Ang.

143
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:00,860
Run! Hurry!

144
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:01,980
Yangyang, Yangyang.

145
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:03,140
Dad, Mom.

146
00:11:03,140 --> 00:11:04,540
Jicai, hurry up.

147
00:11:04,540 --> 00:11:06,460
Dad, Mom, we can't let them go.

148
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:20,860
Hurry, hurry.

149
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,750
Hurry.

150
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,300
Hurry, Jicai.

151
00:11:40,420 --> 00:11:41,460
Let's go, Li Ang.

152
00:11:43,380 --> 00:11:44,780
How dare you stop me?

153
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:46,540
Don't come any closer.

154
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:48,020
Dad, take care of Yangyang.

155
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:50,500
Run!

156
00:11:50,500 --> 00:11:51,340
Gongcai!

157
00:11:57,820 --> 00:11:58,980
- Shaojie!
- Dad!

158
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:00,200
- I'll fight you!
- Mom.

159
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:05,100
Li Ang, let's go.

160
00:12:05,100 --> 00:12:07,100
Lin Yan disfigured me.

161
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:08,100
You shall pay

162
00:12:08,740 --> 00:12:10,020
for his crime.

163
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:28,780
- Lin Yan.
- Jicai.

164
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:30,020
Let Li Ang go,

165
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,420
or I'll kill her.

166
00:12:31,420 --> 00:12:32,290
No.

167
00:12:32,290 --> 00:12:33,140
Let her go.

168
00:12:33,140 --> 00:12:33,980
Let him go.

169
00:12:35,780 --> 00:12:36,700
Release him.

170
00:12:40,340 --> 00:12:41,180
Mr. Lin.

171
00:12:58,940 --> 00:12:59,940
Let her go.

172
00:13:00,980 --> 00:13:01,820
Don't move.

173
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:02,940
I'll take her place.

174
00:13:03,300 --> 00:13:04,140
Cui Che,

175
00:13:05,500 --> 00:13:06,940
I was soft-hearted back then

176
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:08,980
and spared your life.

177
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:10,020
Today,

178
00:13:10,670 --> 00:13:12,060
I'll give you my life.

179
00:13:12,460 --> 00:13:13,580
Let him go.

180
00:13:13,980 --> 00:13:14,820
Father.

181
00:13:14,940 --> 00:13:15,790
Don't move.

182
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:18,340
Let him go.

183
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:20,740
Let him go!

184
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:38,100
- No.
- Leave.

185
00:13:38,100 --> 00:13:39,100
Father.

186
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:40,060
Go!

187
00:13:49,060 --> 00:13:49,980
Leave now.

188
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,140
Let go of Jicai.

189
00:13:55,380 --> 00:13:56,300
Release her.

190
00:13:56,580 --> 00:13:58,180
- Auntie.
- I'll take her place.

191
00:13:58,420 --> 00:13:59,260
Don't move.

192
00:14:00,140 --> 00:14:00,980
Today,

193
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:03,020
I'm in a dead end.

194
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,060
I'll have

195
00:14:07,700 --> 00:14:09,020
the woman you cherish most

196
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,260
accompany me in death.

197
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:18,340
- Jicai!
- Jicai!

198
00:14:48,980 --> 00:14:54,130
♪Like a sunken boat in a dark current,
not a single light of night is seen♪

199
00:14:55,470 --> 00:15:01,680
♪Ahead is hazy,
light and shadow interlaced♪

200
00:15:04,900 --> 00:15:05,740
Your Highness,

201
00:15:06,020 --> 00:15:08,180
if we spare Cui Che
just because he resembles

202
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:09,140
the late heir,

203
00:15:09,860 --> 00:15:11,270
it could lead to endless troubles.

204
00:15:11,290 --> 00:15:16,600
♪Falling into fog, tracking blindly♪

205
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:17,460
Father...

206
00:15:17,620 --> 00:15:18,580
Father!

207
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:22,160
♪If not for thoughts stirring the heart,
again provoking strife♪

208
00:15:22,640 --> 00:15:25,640
♪How would I know it's so unfathomable♪

209
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:28,540
Father!

210
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:30,900
Father is here.

211
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:32,500
Father is here.

212
00:15:35,380 --> 00:15:36,420
Father is here.

213
00:15:37,540 --> 00:15:38,380
Don't worry.

214
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:39,940
With me here,

215
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:41,220
you'll be fine.

216
00:15:42,950 --> 00:15:44,420
No one will bully you.

217
00:15:44,420 --> 00:15:46,150
♪Is it still there♪

218
00:15:46,260 --> 00:15:52,340
♪Luckily, you stay here for me
like a light from afar♪

219
00:15:52,740 --> 00:15:55,510
♪Accompanying me
through the dark thickets♪

220
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:58,440
♪Flattening the deep ravines♪

221
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:02,640
♪Letting me share your glory♪

222
00:16:02,640 --> 00:16:07,350
♪Free from fear and worries
in the cold wind♪

223
00:16:07,770 --> 00:16:11,210
♪You're protecting me by my side♪

224
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:15,850
♪Holding your hand,
I no longer feel empty♪

225
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:22,260
♪Until we walk through the long,
cold winter♪

226
00:16:22,760 --> 00:16:26,200
♪May there be♪

227
00:16:26,540 --> 00:16:30,250
♪No more strangers♪

228
00:16:30,250 --> 00:16:35,770
♪May the dawn never set♪

229
00:17:53,980 --> 00:17:55,860
(Shen's Diner)

230
00:17:55,860 --> 00:17:56,700
Lift it.

231
00:17:56,860 --> 00:17:58,260
Lift it a bit.

232
00:17:58,320 --> 00:17:59,220
To the right.

233
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:01,360
To the right. Push it in.

234
00:18:02,110 --> 00:18:03,390
Why are you so clumsy?

235
00:18:03,470 --> 00:18:04,320
You...

236
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:05,420
Smooth out

237
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:06,900
that red silk.

238
00:18:07,300 --> 00:18:09,300
Don't move. Let me see.

239
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:10,740
(Shen's Diner)
How does it look?

240
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:12,860
Good, just right.

241
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:14,940
I heard your family
has achieved great merit,

242
00:18:15,260 --> 00:18:17,100
and the Emperor inscribed this plaque.

243
00:18:17,660 --> 00:18:19,180
The Emperor and the Princess

244
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:20,820
praised your dishes

245
00:18:21,060 --> 00:18:22,430
as the best in the world.

246
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,530
The best in the world?

247
00:18:23,820 --> 00:18:24,780
I must taste

248
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:26,020
these dishes so highly praised

249
00:18:26,020 --> 00:18:27,260
by the Emperor.

250
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:28,220
Indeed.

251
00:18:28,220 --> 00:18:29,350
The Grand Princess

252
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:30,500
also recommended it.

253
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:31,660
(Recommended by the Princess)

254
00:18:31,660 --> 00:18:33,060
(Best Food in Yong'an: Shen's Diner)

255
00:18:33,060 --> 00:18:34,180
(Recommended by the Emperor)

256
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,660
Why not come in and taste it?

257
00:18:35,660 --> 00:18:36,500
Sure.

258
00:18:36,660 --> 00:18:38,220
Congratulations.

259
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,590
Give it a try.

260
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:43,720
Congratulations.

261
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,780
Thank you.

262
00:18:45,380 --> 00:18:47,730
(Xuanzheng Gate)

263
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:50,160
The former Prefect, Cui Ning,

264
00:18:50,860 --> 00:18:52,380
was honest, loyal,

265
00:18:52,820 --> 00:18:54,220
and righteous.

266
00:18:54,820 --> 00:18:57,460
All his past grievances
have been cleared.

267
00:18:57,980 --> 00:19:00,540
The good name of the Cui family
shall be restored.

268
00:19:00,860 --> 00:19:02,260
Prince Zhao was the true culprit

269
00:19:02,420 --> 00:19:05,060
behind the post-selling case
17 years ago,

270
00:19:05,620 --> 00:19:07,460
and he conspired with Noble Consort Dou

271
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:09,100
in treason.

272
00:19:09,460 --> 00:19:10,780
Now demoted to commoners,

273
00:19:11,020 --> 00:19:12,120
they've both been executed.

274
00:19:12,740 --> 00:19:16,180
All those in the court
who were involved with them

275
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:17,860
have been sentenced accordingly.

276
00:19:18,420 --> 00:19:19,580
Thanks to Your Majesty,

277
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:21,560
the loyal and righteous

278
00:19:21,860 --> 00:19:24,140
have finally seen
their grievances redressed.

279
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:27,660
Rise.

280
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:31,700
Thank you, Your Majesty.

281
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:34,460
Your Majesty,

282
00:19:34,780 --> 00:19:37,020
the Cui case is truly lamentable,

283
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:39,300
but it is my duty

284
00:19:39,310 --> 00:19:41,570
to impeach the Vice Prefect
of the Prefecture,

285
00:19:41,570 --> 00:19:42,420
Lin Yan.

286
00:19:42,670 --> 00:19:44,300
Lin Yan is actually Cui Che.

287
00:19:44,780 --> 00:19:45,740
When he achieved merit

288
00:19:45,740 --> 00:19:47,020
and governed the Capital,

289
00:19:47,210 --> 00:19:48,900
