on putting them in a painting.

577
00:34:22,420 --> 00:34:23,460
That's right.

578
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:26,020
It's like taking a wedding photo.

579
00:34:26,020 --> 00:34:27,940
My hair is standing on end.

580
00:34:27,940 --> 00:34:28,980
Exactly.

581
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:30,340
It's terrifying.

582
00:34:38,010 --> 00:34:38,860
Mr. Lin.

583
00:34:38,860 --> 00:34:39,700
The painting is done.

584
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:18,820
This...

585
00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:21,220
Isn't this the one hanging
in the ancestral hall?

586
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:28,260
(Portrait of Lin Yan, Vice Prefect)

587
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:32,620
Could it be

588
00:35:33,090 --> 00:35:35,100
that we are witnessing history here?

589
00:35:36,260 --> 00:35:37,220
No way.

590
00:35:40,420 --> 00:35:41,260
Jicai.

591
00:35:41,740 --> 00:35:42,580
Jicai,

592
00:35:42,780 --> 00:35:44,160
stand up straight, lift your head,

593
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:45,320
and tuck in your chin a bit.

594
00:35:45,380 --> 00:35:47,060
Imagine there's an apple
under your chin.

595
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:48,220
You'll look better that way.

596
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:49,500
Yes, listen to your mom.

597
00:35:49,500 --> 00:35:51,850
Hold that apple and you'll look good.

598
00:35:51,850 --> 00:35:52,700
Right, right.

599
00:35:52,700 --> 00:35:54,660
Turn your head to the side a bit.

600
00:35:54,660 --> 00:35:55,700
You look fatter this way.

601
00:35:55,820 --> 00:35:56,660
Turn a bit more.

602
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:05,780
Jicai, turn a bit more to this side.

603
00:36:06,100 --> 00:36:07,580
You forgot about the apple again.

604
00:36:07,580 --> 00:36:09,260
You have to hold the apple to look good.

605
00:36:09,260 --> 00:36:10,860
Too much. Come back a bit.

606
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:12,340
You look better when you smile.

607
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:14,540
- Expression.
- Show some emotion.

608
00:36:14,540 --> 00:36:15,740
You look better when you smile.

609
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:16,940
Hold it.

610
00:36:17,420 --> 00:36:19,020
Your expression needs to be there.

611
00:36:19,300 --> 00:36:20,140
Like this.

612
00:36:20,890 --> 00:36:21,740
This is good enough.

613
00:36:21,740 --> 00:36:22,580
This is good.

614
00:36:23,260 --> 00:36:24,100
Hurry up and paint.

615
00:36:24,730 --> 00:36:25,580
Why this pose?

616
00:36:25,580 --> 00:36:26,540
You...

617
00:36:26,540 --> 00:36:27,380
Never mind.

618
00:36:27,380 --> 00:36:28,860
Let her be.

619
00:37:08,300 --> 00:37:09,660
Mr. Lin, the painting is done.

620
00:37:11,060 --> 00:37:11,900
Thank you.

621
00:37:12,380 --> 00:37:13,420
I'll take my leave now.

622
00:37:25,660 --> 00:37:26,740
It feels

623
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:28,340
like something is off.

624
00:37:28,340 --> 00:37:29,660
Yes, it is.

625
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:31,940
Jicai, come here and take a look.

626
00:37:32,100 --> 00:37:33,640
- It looks very much like you.
- Come.

627
00:37:34,620 --> 00:37:36,060
I can't quite put my finger on it,

628
00:37:36,060 --> 00:37:38,100
but something feels off.

629
00:37:38,260 --> 00:37:39,180
A bit fat, maybe?

630
00:37:39,580 --> 00:37:40,580
No, it's not fat.

631
00:37:40,580 --> 00:37:41,540
It's just...

632
00:37:51,930 --> 00:37:55,290
♪Wear a sunset glow upon the brow♪

633
00:37:55,290 --> 00:37:58,530
♪Breeze sways,
wind chimes hang below the cloud♪

634
00:37:58,850 --> 00:38:01,890
♪Hear one chime ring,
tugging at the heart♪

635
00:38:01,890 --> 00:38:04,970
♪True feelings perhaps
can only be sensed♪

636
00:38:05,570 --> 00:38:08,970
♪Words held back, feelings unrestrained♪

637
00:38:08,970 --> 00:38:14,090
♪Could the road ahead,
let us gaze but not doubt♪

638
00:38:16,050 --> 00:38:19,210
♪Mistook all eyes see as cold ice♪

639
00:38:19,210 --> 00:38:22,610
♪Yet let dusk dye
the ears and temples red♪

640
00:38:22,850 --> 00:38:25,890
♪Even holding breath
couldn't help but stop♪

641
00:38:25,890 --> 00:38:28,970
♪Exposing my warmed heart held tight♪

642
00:38:29,530 --> 00:38:33,010
♪Bustling is you, desolate is you♪

643
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:36,370
♪Reservedly drawing you into this life♪

644
00:38:36,370 --> 00:38:39,810
♪Hesitating, undecided,
the heart hard to deceive♪

645
00:38:41,060 --> 00:38:41,900
Use the willow branch

646
00:38:42,300 --> 00:38:44,020
to blur that pose.

647
00:38:45,890 --> 00:38:48,540
♪When rushing to you,
leaving my deep thoughts in disarray♪

648
00:38:48,540 --> 00:38:50,350
(Portrait of Lady Shen,
Lin Yan's only wife)

649
00:38:50,350 --> 00:38:53,550
♪Gazing at you with deep affection,
until your figure fades♪

650
00:38:53,550 --> 00:38:56,690
♪Heart stirs,
wind swirls the lightest ripples♪

651
00:38:56,690 --> 00:38:59,480
♪A thousand tangled thoughts concealed♪

652
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:00,610
♪Saved a whole lifetime♪

653
00:39:01,300 --> 00:39:02,220
This...

654
00:39:02,220 --> 00:39:03,900
So, the lady in that painting

655
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:04,780
is Jicai.

656
00:39:04,780 --> 00:39:05,620
Yes.

657
00:39:06,860 --> 00:39:07,700
Auntie.

658
00:39:08,320 --> 00:39:10,730
♪What seems beyond reach♪

659
00:39:10,730 --> 00:39:13,400
♪Through life and death changes♪

660
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:14,630
- Auntie.
- No way.

661
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:18,990
♪Only you, never cease, never yield♪

662
00:39:24,180 --> 00:39:25,500
- Ouch.
- What's wrong?

663
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:26,680
- Dad.
- Dad, are you okay?

664
00:39:26,690 --> 00:39:27,580
What's going on?

665
00:39:27,580 --> 00:39:29,220
- Dad, what's wrong?
- What's wrong?

666
00:39:29,220 --> 00:39:31,380
What's going on with your head?

667
00:39:31,380 --> 00:39:32,220
Are you okay?

668
00:39:32,220 --> 00:39:33,900
Gongcai.

669
00:39:34,460 --> 00:39:35,960
- Should you lie down?
- How are you?

670
00:39:35,970 --> 00:39:37,060
What happened?

671
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:41,740
Lady Shen and her husband
are deeply in love,

672
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:43,540
envied by others.

673
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:45,860
You brat.

674
00:39:46,180 --> 00:39:47,260
You're not listening again.

675
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:50,060
If it weren't for Jicai going to class,

676
00:39:50,060 --> 00:39:51,500
I wouldn't even bother with you.

677
00:39:52,620 --> 00:39:53,460
Sit up straight.

678
00:39:55,340 --> 00:39:56,580
If you keep doing this.

679
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,500
I won't tell you

680
00:39:58,500 --> 00:40:00,620
the most crucial truth.

681
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:02,180
Don't tell me then.

682
00:40:04,380 --> 00:40:05,340
How about this?

683
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:07,140
As we agreed before,

684
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:09,540
is that okay?

685
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:11,660
Grandpa, you have to give me 3 yuan.

686
00:40:11,660 --> 00:40:12,940
You brat.

687
00:40:12,940 --> 00:40:14,220
Just like your dad.

688
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:15,980
Alright, sit down.

689
00:40:16,500 --> 00:40:17,820
Let me tell you.

690
00:40:20,130 --> 00:40:22,460
The most crucial truth is

691
00:40:22,900 --> 00:40:24,320
that it's all fake.

692
00:40:31,980 --> 00:40:34,100
Well, not exactly fake.

693
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:35,220
The story

694
00:40:35,420 --> 00:40:36,980
is still real.

695
00:40:37,180 --> 00:40:38,700
The Vice Prefect

696
00:40:38,970 --> 00:40:42,580
did marry a lady surnamed Shen,

697
00:40:42,580 --> 00:40:44,980
but she was not our ancestor.

698
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,990
Our true ancestor

699
00:40:47,300 --> 00:40:52,060
is actually a friend of Mr. Lin,

700
00:40:52,060 --> 00:40:54,580
Censor Pei Fei.

701
00:40:55,220 --> 00:40:56,340
Mr. Pei later

702
00:40:56,340 --> 00:40:58,580
married into our family.

703
00:40:59,180 --> 00:41:00,540
But I don't think

704
00:41:00,540 --> 00:41:04,060
he is as impressive as Mr. Lin,

705
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:04,940
so

706
00:41:05,150 --> 00:41:07,100
I deliberately said that.

707
00:41:08,010 --> 00:41:09,030
I remember now.

708
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:10,420
I remember now.

709
00:41:10,420 --> 00:41:11,260
What is it?

710
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:13,980
Our ancestor

711
00:41:13,980 --> 00:41:15,420
was never Mr. Lin.

712
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:17,100
It was Pei Fei.

713
00:41:17,100 --> 00:41:18,660
- What?
- Pei Fei?

714
00:41:18,660 --> 00:41:20,500
Grandpa thought Mr. Lin
was more impressive,

715
00:41:20,500 --> 00:41:21,700
so he deliberately said that.

716
00:41:21,930 --> 00:41:22,820
Jicai,

717
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:24,140
there is absolutely no relation

718
00:41:24,140 --> 00:41:25,340
between you and Mr. Lin.

719
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,880
You two can get married.

